	<p>Sign in to have your submissions assigned to you and generally tinker with stuff. Signing in will allow you to edit you submissions in the future.</p>

	<p>Sign in using your OpenID or your 
	<a href="$site_information.url/openid/login?openid_claimed_identity=google.com/accounts/o8/id">Google</a>, 
